track.name: These Days
comments: Beautiful. And tragic, almost hard to hear... [2]
Violent colors so obscene,, thay line hits hard I love it!!!
They bring the God of the blues right next to you to inhale your second hand smoke late at night
Beautiful. And tragic, almost hard to hear...
After listening to this track I need a moment of silence... This is one of those golden tracks that evoke that kind of feeling.

"The little house on Ellis Drive 
Is where I felt most alive 
The oak tree covered that old Ford 
I miss it Lord, I miss it Lord ..... "                    
Amazing ....just amazing...
Its 2 am, cigarrette in hand and this comes on, never heard it before but i will listen to it on every quiet night from now on.
I miss it Lord, I miss it Lord.
